Faust 64  / 29.04.2014 11:05 / gefundenToday the female part of our team had to go for the Cache of the Day alone, the male part had too much work to do! This was the cache she chose for the 288th day of our "Longest Streak"!The cache was found without problems, no long search, no muggels around - the container and the logbook are in good condition!Nice place, it's great to see, that this area has a cache again - years ago we came here several times to find golfpro's "Ramstein - Royal - BLUE - TB Swap Box" which was hidden nearby and to swap trackables.TFTC, no trade this time, signed the log at 11.05 am, greets,Faust 64 (only the female part of the team, the male part had rehearsals at the Palatinate Theatre)# 4749
